European Stocks Decline; Retailers, Banks Lead Benchmark Stoxx 600 Lower

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-04-27T07:29:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/european-stocks-decline-retailers-banks-lead-benchmark-stoxx-600-lower.html
European stocks fell for the first
time in five days as retailers and banks retreated. The Stoxx
Europe 600 Index declined 0.2 percent to 280.76 at 8:28 a.m. in
 London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
